    expression treated as *.*
 4. *.*|*.bak|*.tmp
    The character | can be used in the mask only once,
    expression treated as *.*|*.bak
 5. |*.bak
    The same as *|*.bak
 6. *.*|/^pict\d{1,3}\.gif$/i
    All files except for pict0.gif — pict999.gif, disregard the character case.

